'''天主教巴雷拉斯教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Barreriensis}}；{{lang-pt|Diocese de Barreiras}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]一個[[天主教|天主教]][[教區|教區]]，位於[[巴伊亞州|巴伊亞州]]西北部。此教區屬[[天主教費拉迪聖安娜總教區|費拉迪聖安娜總教區]]。

教區成立於1979年5月21日。<ref>{{cite web |title=BARRERIENSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19790521_barreriensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009161934/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19790521_barreriensis.html |archivedate=2019-10-09 |language=la |date=1979-05-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年有教友320,000人，佔總人口90.1%。有二十個堂區、司鐸廿四人。教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 09.10.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/09/191009a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191009141444/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/09/191009a.html |archivedate=2019-10-09 |language=en |date=2019-10-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

